text: President Joe Biden’s day one approach to immigration included blanket amnesty and halting border wall construction.

Says a video shows Joe Biden boasted in 2006 about voting for ‘700 miles of fence’ and talking about immigration in some entirely different ways than he does today.
Biden administration is continuing construction of border wall
